{"tid":1931910,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"專家料武肺病毒早晚在非洲社區擴散","createTime":"2020-03-18T11:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T13:13:51.000Z","uid":83713,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dbf859cf31bf4345efa8143af50037a6f9fffd77","tid":1931910,"uid":83713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T11:50:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=384784\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D384784&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqF5q%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=d696e40e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D384784&h=76da4e0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=384784</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎肆虐，過半撒哈拉以南的非洲國家都已出現疫情，確診個案超過160宗。雖然數遠低於歐美等國，但專家指非洲的醫療系統脆弱，加上缺乏資源，疫情可能在當地閃電式擴散。<br />\n<br />\n撒哈拉以南的非洲國家中，南非暫時是最受武肺病毒疫情影響的國家，確診病例已經超過80宗。當地已進入國家災難狀態，並實施旅行禁令和關閉學校等措施，遏止病毒擴散。<br />\n<br />\n連同南非，撒哈拉以南有逾半，即大約27個國家出現確診病例，大多是輸入病例，但專家認為病毒向社區蔓延只是時間問題。<br />\n<br />\n世界衛生組織早前指出，非洲只有8個國家能應對今次疫情，即使部分國家經歷過伊波拉疫情後，醫療系統已有改善，但仍然不足。<br />\n<br />\n非洲疾病控制及預防中心承認，當地不少國家的醫療系統脆弱，無能力快速找出確診患者將他們隔離，以阻止病毒擴散，又缺乏足夠經驗的醫護人員和醫療設備，例如呼吸輔助器等，而且醫院早已因為瘧疾等致命傳染病而超負荷，加上戰亂的破壞，<span style=\"color: red;\">以內戰持續5年的南蘇丹為例，政府只有24張隔離病床，一旦出現大量武肺冠狀病毒患者，院方根本應付不來。</span><br />\n<br />\n家居隔離都不可行，因為很多非洲家庭，都是一家幾口迫在狹小房間，還要共用公眾水龍頭、廁所。<br />\n<br />\n鼓勵民眾連勤洗手保持衞生亦不切實際，在有超過1200萬人口的東非，很多人都無自來水，甚至窮得連肥皂都負擔不來。<br />\n<br />\n專家警告，一旦病毒入侵環境惡劣和擠迫的非洲貧困地區，將會以閃電式的速度擴散。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n奶開共實有抗體，唔怕啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f4f0d4bedb57e6a9d502ad0a9089e585e1e61d","tid":1931910,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T11:53:01.000Z","msg":"成個洲玩撚完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c9811908580ce27c25b373ec269c0e344e760bd","tid":1931910,"uid":150483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"73f4f0d4bedb57e6a9d502ad0a9089e585e1e61d","tid":1931910,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T11:53:01.000Z","msg":"成個洲玩撚完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T11:54:27.000Z","msg":"內戰咗3，40年<br />\n今次齊心抗疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751cdc56f512d8331f89e69b133d533b7306195a","tid":1931910,"uid":240374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T11:55:12.000Z","msg":"矛盾大對決<br />\n絕對會感染前死vs 會對會係你死前傳染"},{"pid":"9568a80b13e12fd0969104f167bd315d9a94283d","tid":1931910,"uid":112622,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T11:56:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03f53041f21d3844f1e627d82ffd78724209e0f3","tid":1931910,"uid":107023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:47:26.000Z","msg":"咪岩，清洗地球人口"},{"pid":"6baa9c1d3e157dc35ce5d7b14728e9f7262b29f7","tid":1931910,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03f53041f21d3844f1e627d82ffd78724209e0f3","tid":1931910,"uid":107023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:47:26.000Z","msg":"咪岩，清洗地球人口"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8abe0a6fc8e7cc04a5a1d966e1136fba223f6ae9","tid":1931910,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9568a80b13e12fd0969104f167bd315d9a94283d","tid":1931910,"uid":112622,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T11:56:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:50:20.000Z","msg":"埃塞俄比亞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc68b4b505cfcc8de159d6998d6d9b8537f862f0","tid":1931910,"uid":232250,"like